(3, 'Canteen', '<div class=\"gdlr-core-pbf-element\">\n<h5>&ldquo;It is everyone&#39;s birthright to enjoy the fruits of all their hard work; this is a blessing from God&rdquo;.</h5>\n\n<p>The college canteen features vast facilities. The students and employees of the college are provided with the hygiene and quality South and North Indian food as well as confectionaries. There is a spacious kitchen in the campus canteen, and culinary employees take particular care to serve nutritious and delicious cuisine for students and staff. Reverse osmosis purified water is used to prepare food items and drinking purpose.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"inspect-element-top-layer\" style=\"pointer-events: none; border: unset; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div data-inspect-element=\"inspectElement\" id=\"inspect-element-top-layer\" popover=\"auto\" style=\"pointer-events: none; border: unset; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</div>', '2rybkg5kv7cwgsogsg.jpeg', 'i6ir30pou1c8wo8wg4.jpeg', '', 1);
