rowspan=\"6\">6608AM</td>\n			<td style=\"width:233px\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">Upon completion of the course student will be able to</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:63px; width:233px\">1</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">learn to demonstrate a critical understanding of key concepts in disaster risk reduction and<br />\n			humanitarian response</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:63px; width:233px\">2</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">critically evaluate disaster risk reduction and humanitarian response policy and practice from<br />\n			multiple perspectives.</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:63px; width:233px\">3</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">develop an understanding of standards of humanitarian response and practical relevance in<br />\n			specific types of disasters and conflict situations</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:42px; width:233px\">4</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">critically understand the strengths and weaknesses of disaster management approaches</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:63px; width:233px\">5</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">planning and programming in different countries, particularly their home country or the countries<br />\n			they work in</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"height:40px; width:201px\">Course</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\">Course Code</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:233px\">Course Outcome Number</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:383px\">Course Outcome</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td rowspan=\"5\" style=\"height:189px; width:201px\">ADVANCED DRUG DELIVERY SYSTEMS LAB</td>\n			<td rowspan=\"5\">660803</td>\n			<td style=\"width:233px\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">Upon completion of the course student will be able to</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"height:42px; width:233px\">1</td>\n			<td style=\"width:383px\">Know the Study on diffusion of drugs through various polymeric membr